        "content": "<p>Infinite sets of natural numbers don't have decidable equality I guess. There are infinitely many things to check. You can look into <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Finset#doc\">docs#Finset</a></p>",
