    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"515324\">@An Qi Zhang</span> you're mixing up \"defining equality\" with \"deciding equality\". Equality has already been defined, which is why you could even write <code>=</code> in the first place.</p>",
